---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | RecycleOldTech - Electronics Recycling Directory" 
  description="Learn about our mission to promote responsible electronics recycling and protect the environment. Find certified e-waste centers nationwide."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-green-900 via-green-800 to-green-700">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white text-center mb-6">Our Mission</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-50 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Connecting people with certified electronics recycling centers to protect our environment and promote responsible e-waste disposal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why We Exist</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            RecycleOldTech was founded with a simple yet crucial mission. We aim to make electronics recycling accessible to everyone. In today's world, electronic devices are increasingly integral to our daily lives. Proper disposal of outdated or broken electronics has never been more important.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Every year, millions of tons of electronic waste end up in landfills. This releases harmful toxins into our environment. We believe that by making it easier to find certified recycling centers, we can help reduce this environmental impact. Our goal is to promote responsible e-waste management across the United States.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Our team is committed to providing accurate, up-to-date information. We help individuals and businesses make informed decisions about electronics recycling. We thoroughly research and verify all recycling centers in our directory. This ensures they meet environmental and safety standards.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Electronics Lifecycle Challenge</h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Modern Consumer Patterns</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The rapid pace of technological advancement has created unprecedented challenges in electronics disposal. Consumer behavior patterns show that people replace devices more frequently than ever before. Smartphones are typically replaced every 2-3 years. Laptops and computers have an average lifespan of 4-5 years. This constant upgrade cycle generates massive amounts of electronic waste.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Replacement Frequency</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Smartphones: Every 2-3 years</li>
                  <li>• Tablets: Every 3-4 years</li>
                  <li>• Laptops: Every 4-5 years</li>
                  <li>• Desktop computers: Every 5-6 years</li>
                  <li>• Televisions: Every 7-10 years</li>
                  <li>• Gaming consoles: Every 6-8 years</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Disposal Challenges</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Complex material composition</li>
                  <li>• Miniaturization makes separation difficult</li>
                  <li>• Hazardous substances require special handling</li>
                  <li>• Limited consumer awareness of proper disposal</li>
                  <li>• Inconvenient recycling locations</li>
                  <li>• Data security concerns</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Growing E-Waste Problem</h2>
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-4">Alarming Statistics</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-3">Global Impact</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• 54 million tons of e-waste generated globally each year</li>
                  <li>• Only 20% of e-waste is properly recycled worldwide</li>
                  <li>• E-waste is the fastest-growing waste stream</li>
                  <li>• Contains over 1,000 different toxic substances</li>
                  <li>• Expected to reach 74 million tons by 2030</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-3">US Specific Data</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• 6.9 billion pounds of e-waste generated annually</li>
                  <li>• Average American discards 44 pounds of e-waste yearly</li>
                  <li>• Only 25% of e-waste is recycled in the US</li>
                  <li>• $60 billion worth of raw materials wasted</li>
                  <li>• 9.4 million tons could be diverted from landfills</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            The exponential growth of electronic waste poses a significant threat to our environment. Toxic materials like lead, mercury, cadmium, and brominated flame retardants leak into soil and groundwater. This contamination affects local ecosystems and human health. The situation requires immediate action from individuals, businesses, and governments.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-3">Health and Environmental Consequences</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Improper e-waste disposal has far-reaching consequences beyond environmental damage:</p>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Neurological damage from lead exposure</li>
              <li>• Respiratory problems from toxic fume inhalation</li>
              <li>• Birth defects in communities near disposal sites</li>
              <li>• Contaminated water supplies affecting millions</li>
              <li>• Soil degradation making agriculture impossible</li>
              <li>• Wildlife population decline and ecosystem disruption</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Solution</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Comprehensive Directory</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Our platform features the most extensive database of certified electronics recycling centers in the United States. We provide detailed information about each facility.</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• Location and contact details</li>
                <li>• Accepted electronics types</li>
                <li>• Recycling certifications</li>
                <li>• Operating hours and fees</li>
                <li>• Special services offered</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Rigorous Verification</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We don't just list any recycling center. Our team conducts thorough research and verification to ensure quality and reliability.</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• R2 and e-Stewards certification checks</li>
                <li>• EPA compliance verification</li>
                <li>• State licensing confirmation</li>
                <li>• Data security protocol validation</li>
                <li>• Environmental impact assessment</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-blue-200 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6">How Our Platform Works</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Search by Location</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Enter your zip code or city to find nearby recycling centers. Our database covers all 50 states with thousands of verified locations.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">2</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Filter by Device Type</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Select the electronics you need to recycle. View centers that accept your specific devices and any special requirements.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">3</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Get Detailed Information</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Access contact details, hours, pricing, and preparation instructions. Make informed decisions about your recycling options.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Impact</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">40000+</div>
              <div class="text-gray-700">Recycling Centers</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">50</div>
              <div class="text-gray-700">States Covered</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">24/7</div>
              <div class="text-gray-700">Access</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Environmental Benefits We've Facilitated</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600 mb-3">Resource Conservation</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Millions of pounds of materials diverted from landfills</li>
                  <li>• Thousands of tons of precious metals recovered</li>
                  <li>• Significant reduction in mining for new materials</li>
                  <li>• Energy savings equivalent to powering homes</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600 mb-3">Environmental Protection</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Prevention of toxic chemical release</li>
                  <li>• Groundwater contamination prevention</li>
                  <li>• Reduction in greenhouse gas emissions</li>
                  <li>• Protection of local ecosystems</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Industry Partnerships and Certifications</h2>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6">Working with Industry Leaders</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Our success depends on strong partnerships with recycling industry leaders, environmental organizations, and technology companies. These collaborations ensure our directory remains current and our standards remain high. We work directly with certification bodies to verify recycling center credentials.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-3">Certification Partners</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Responsible Recycling (R2) Standard</li>
                  <li>• e-Stewards Certification Program</li>
                  <li>• Environmental Protection Agency (EPA)</li>
                  <li>• National Association for Information Destruction (NAID)</li>
                  <li>• International Association of Electronics Recyclers (IAER)</li>
                  <li>• Sustainable Electronics Initiative (SEI)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-3">Technology Partners</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Major electronics manufacturers</li>
                  <li>• Cloud service providers for data security</li>
                  <li>• Mapping and location service providers</li>
                  <li>• Payment processing companies</li>
                  <li>• Data analytics and reporting platforms</li>
                  <li>• Mobile app development partners</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Team and Values</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Who We Are</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Our team consists of environmental scientists, technology experts, and sustainability advocates. We share a common passion for protecting the environment through responsible technology disposal. Our diverse backgrounds bring unique perspectives to solving the e-waste challenge.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We work with recycling industry professionals, environmental organizations, and government agencies. This collaboration ensures our directory remains current and reliable. We continuously update our database to reflect changes in the recycling landscape.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Core Values</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                  <div>
                    <strong class="text-gray-900">Transparency:</strong>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"> We provide clear, honest information about recycling centers and processes.</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                  <div>
                    <strong class="text-gray-900">Reliability:</strong>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"> Our verification process ensures all listed centers meet strict standards.</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                  <div>
                    <strong class="text-gray-900">Accessibility:</strong>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"> We make responsible recycling easy and convenient for everyone.</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                  <div>
                    <strong class="text-gray-900">Innovation:</strong>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"> We continuously improve our platform to better serve users and the environment.</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Commitment</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="mt-1 bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Verified Centers</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We only list certified recycling centers that meet strict environmental and safety standards. Every facility undergoes rigorous verification before inclusion in our directory.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="mt-1 bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Easy Access</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our platform makes it simple to find the nearest recycling center. We provide detailed information about their services, making recycling convenient for everyone.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="mt-1 bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Environmental Impact</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We're dedicated to reducing e-waste in landfills and promoting sustainable recycling practices. Our mission extends beyond directory services to education and advocacy.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="mt-1 bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Continuous Improvement</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We regularly update our platform with new features and information. User feedback helps us improve the recycling experience and expand our impact.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Future Goals</h2>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6">Looking Ahead</h3>
