                  <li>• International directory expansion</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-3">Educational Initiatives</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>• School recycling education programs</li>
                  <li>• Community awareness campaigns</li>
                  <li>• Business sustainability consulting</li>
                  <li>• Government policy advocacy</li>
                  <li>• Research collaboration projects</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Join Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Whether you're an individual looking to recycle old electronics or a business seeking responsible disposal solutions, we're here to help. Together, we can make a significant impact on reducing e-waste. We can protect our environment for future generations through responsible recycling practices.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
            Every device recycled properly makes a difference. Join thousands of environmentally conscious individuals and businesses. Use our directory to find certified recycling centers in your area. Take action today to protect our planet's future.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Find a Recycling Center
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
